Full Algorithm (Architect View):
================================

START WORKER

loop forever:

  events = read_change_events()

  mark_entities_dirty(events)

  metadata = load_udf_metadata()

  sync_reporting_schema(metadata)

  dirty_entities = fetch_dirty_entities()

  for entity in dirty_entities:
        base = load_entity(entity)
        udfs = load_udf_values(entity)

        row = flatten(base, udfs, metadata)

        normalized_row = type_cast(row)

        upsert_reporting(normalized_row)

        mark_processed(entity)

END LOOP

Core Components:
================
1. Change Detector
2. Metadata Loader
3. Schema Manager
4. Data Transformer
5. Upsert Writer
6. Sync Tracker

